  <brief_title>Effect of Violent First-Person Shooter (FPS) Video Games on Shooting Accuracy</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;Boom, Headshot!&quot;: Violent First-Person Shooter (FPS) Video Games That Reward Headshots Train Individuals to Aim for the Head When Shooting a Realistic Firearm</official_title>
